description:
Take a look at the 20th Anniversary 'Cementing a Legacy' Trailer for Halo 2, a legendary installment in the sci-fi first-person shooter franchise developed by Bungie. Players have braved the battles, forged unbreakable bonds, and created unforgettable memories within Halo 2. Hear from fans around the world rave about their favorite moments across all of Halo 2 for the last 20 years. Halo 2 is available now within Halo: The Master Chief Collection for Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.

#Halo2 #HaloTheMasterChiefCollection #Gaming
title: Halo 2 - Official 20th Anniversary 'Cementing a Legacy' Trailer

description:
Check out the SNK Collaboration Update Trailer for Dungeon Fighter Online, a free-to-play anime RPG beat-em-up developed by Neople. Players will step into the dungeons of DFO and encounter the iconic fighters of the SNK universe through a series of special events, exhilarating new game modes, and unique Avatars. Dungeon Fighter Online is available now for PC.

#DungeonFighterOnline #SNK #Collaboration
title: Dungeon Fighter Online x SNK - Official Collaboration Update Trailer
